I know you wrote on
the Zone and the --

00:21:23.149 --> 00:21:25.051 align:middle line:90%
getting into the abundant zone.

00:21:25.051 --> 00:21:26.753 align:middle line:90%
Getting into this lucky zone.

00:21:26.753 --> 00:21:29.322 align:middle line:84%
Is that related to
the time conversation?

00:21:29.322 --> 00:21:30.590 align:middle line:90%
Or not at all?

00:21:30.590 --> 00:21:31.624 align:middle line:90%
>> Evans: Yeah.

00:21:31.624 --> 00:21:32.825 align:middle line:84%
Well basically what
happened was that

00:21:32.825 --> 00:21:34.460 align:middle line:84%
"The Zone" was a book
I wrote this year.

00:21:34.460 --> 00:21:36.662 align:middle line:84%
I started it on the
Spring Equinox.

00:21:36.662 --> 00:21:40.066 align:middle line:84%
And I finished it at
the Summer Solstice.

00:21:40.066 --> 00:21:42.201 align:middle line:84%
So I wrote it in two or
three months, you know?

00:21:42.201 --> 00:21:44.070 align:middle line:84%
And it's about the
zones we get into.

00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:46.339 align:middle line:84%
And I started to explore
this concept of zones.

00:21:46.339 --> 00:21:48.174 align:middle line:84%
You know, when you're
"In the zone".

00:21:48.174 --> 00:21:49.542 align:middle line:84%
And I realized that
you can put --

00:21:49.542 --> 00:21:52.478 align:middle line:84%
with the word "zone" you can
put in nearly any English word.

00:21:52.478 --> 00:21:54.046 align:middle line:84%
You know, you can
have the aardvark zone

00:21:54.046 --> 00:21:54.981 align:middle line:90%
or the banana zone.

00:21:54.981 --> 00:21:57.250 align:middle line:90%
Or the child zone.

00:21:57.250 --> 00:21:59.752 align:middle line:84%
And so I picked lots
of nice things

00:21:59.752 --> 00:22:00.686 align:middle line:90%
that go with the word zone.

00:22:00.686 --> 00:22:01.888 align:middle line:90%
Like the productive zone.

00:22:01.888 --> 00:22:03.289 align:middle line:90%
Or the entrepreneurial zone.

00:22:03.289 --> 00:22:04.724 align:middle line:90%
The creative zone.

00:22:04.724 --> 00:22:05.925 align:middle line:90%
The performance zone.

00:22:05.925 --> 00:22:08.561 align:middle line:84%
And I realized that also
we end up in danger zones.

00:22:08.561 --> 00:22:11.531 align:middle line:84%
You know, so when
we're in a doing zone,

00:22:11.531 --> 00:22:13.666 align:middle line:84%
and the wheels come off,
we end up in a danger zone.

00:22:13.666 --> 00:22:17.770 align:middle line:84%
And these danger zones might
be guilt or fear or anger.

00:22:17.770 --> 00:22:20.540 align:middle line:84%
And then I came up with the
concept of the healing zone.

00:22:20.540 --> 00:22:22.341 align:middle line:84%
So we can transit
from a danger zone,

00:22:22.341 --> 00:22:24.944 align:middle line:84%
through the healing
zone, into a being zone.

00:22:24.944 --> 00:22:26.746 align:middle line:84%
But what I did when
I was driving --

00:22:26.746 --> 00:22:27.747 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Because
they're all happening

00:22:27.747 --> 00:22:29.115 align:middle line:90%
at the same time, aren't they?

00:22:29.115 --> 00:22:30.716 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Yeah we can be in
multiple zones at the same time.

00:22:30.716 --> 00:22:36.055 align:middle line:84%
So let's say you're doing a new
business online and you want

00:22:36.055 --> 00:22:39.425 align:middle line:84%
to do a business -- a dating
agency -- online dating.

00:22:39.425 --> 00:22:40.927 align:middle line:84%
So you need to be in
the creative zone.

00:22:40.927 --> 00:22:41.761 align:middle line:90%
In the loving zone.

00:22:41.761 --> 00:22:42.762 align:middle line:90%
And in the entrepreneurial zone

00:22:42.762 --> 00:22:44.197 align:middle line:84%
because you're starting
a new business.

00:22:44.197 --> 00:22:46.999 align:middle line:84%
But what happens is people could
end up in multiple danger zones.

00:22:46.999 --> 00:22:48.768 align:middle line:90%
So you might have an addiction.

00:22:48.768 --> 00:22:51.204 align:middle line:84%
And then you might end
up in the addiction zone.

00:22:51.204 --> 00:22:52.572 align:middle line:90%
The anger zone.

00:22:52.572 --> 00:22:54.640 align:middle line:84%
Because you're angry at the
system for having the addiction.

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:57.677 align:middle line:84%
And then you're also in the
guilt zone because you're guilty

00:22:57.677 --> 00:22:59.111 align:middle line:90%
because you've got an addiction.

00:22:59.111 --> 00:23:00.813 align:middle line:84%
So what I've found is,
you can actually --

00:23:00.813 --> 00:23:03.116 align:middle line:84%
I designed these zones -- when
I say I designed these zones,

00:23:03.116 --> 00:23:06.185 align:middle line:84%
I was driving along one day
and not thinking of anything.

00:23:06.185 --> 00:23:08.054 align:middle line:84%
And this idea came
in of a hexagon.

00:23:08.054 --> 00:23:11.390 align:middle line:84%
That every zone's got 6
sides and 6 aspects to it.

00:23:11.390 --> 00:23:13.726 align:middle line:90%
Now a hexagon is brilliant

00:23:13.726 --> 00:23:16.496 align:middle line:84%
because it's great
packing density.

00:23:16.496 --> 00:23:17.864 align:middle line:90%
It's like inside beehives.

00:23:17.864 --> 00:23:21.167 align:middle line:84%
You can put lots of hexagons
together and it's very strong.

00:23:21.167 --> 00:23:23.936 align:middle line:84%
And I realized then with
the hexagons you can create

00:23:23.936 --> 00:23:25.571 align:middle line:90%
super zones.

00:23:25.571 --> 00:23:27.540 align:middle line:84%
And so let's say you've
got some addiction.

00:23:27.540 --> 00:23:32.778 align:middle line:84%
You can surround the addiction
with some being and doing zones

00:23:32.778 --> 00:23:34.881 align:middle line:90%
and it annuls the addiction.

00:23:34.881 --> 00:23:37.283 align:middle line:90%
But also you can create focus.

00:23:37.283 --> 00:23:39.285 align:middle line:84%
So if you want some
more money in your life,

00:23:39.285 --> 00:23:42.788 align:middle line:84%
you can put an energetic symbol
in the middle of the zone,

00:23:42.788 --> 00:23:44.590 align:middle line:84%
and surround that
with other stuff.

00:23:44.590 --> 00:23:46.492 align:middle line:84%
And I've got some
magical symbols

00:23:46.492 --> 00:23:48.895 align:middle line:84%
from an esoteric school
I belong to in Germany.

00:23:48.895 --> 00:23:51.531 align:middle line:84%
And I used that as the
generator of abundance.

00:23:51.531 --> 00:23:53.432 align:middle line:90%
Surround it with other zones

00:23:53.432 --> 00:23:56.736 align:middle line:84%
that compliment abundance,
like magic.

00:23:56.736 --> 00:23:57.870 align:middle line:90%
Like creativity.

00:23:57.870 --> 00:23:59.772 align:middle line:84%
Like entrepreneurship,
and this sort of stuff.

00:23:59.772 --> 00:24:01.874 align:middle line:90%
And you put this on your wall.

00:24:01.874 --> 00:24:04.510 align:middle line:84%
And sure enough that magic
leaks into your world.

00:24:04.510 --> 00:24:06.078 align:middle line:84%
And I've got to tell
you this story.

00:24:06.078 --> 00:24:08.814 align:middle line:84%
As I came up with this
idea for hexacombs.

00:24:08.814 --> 00:24:13.085 align:middle line:84%
I was driving home, and I
just turned into my drive.

00:24:13.085 --> 00:24:14.787 align:middle line:84%
And as I did that,
a car came past

00:24:14.787 --> 00:24:18.124 align:middle line:90%
with H-E-X on the number plate.

00:24:18.124 --> 00:24:18.891 align:middle line:90%
Spooky.

00:24:18.891 --> 00:24:19.892 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:24:19.892 --> 00:24:21.661 align:middle line:84%
Yeah. Is there a
danger to play too much

00:24:21.661 --> 00:24:24.363 align:middle line:84%
with all those --
the life itself?

00:24:24.363 --> 00:24:26.432 align:middle line:84%
You know, that it
kind of backfires?

00:24:26.432 --> 00:24:27.767 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Yeah I think
if you hold fear.

00:24:27.767 --> 00:24:30.536 align:middle line:84%
Say if you have fear that
things are going to go wrong,

00:24:30.536 --> 00:24:31.470 align:middle line:90%
then they will go wrong.

00:24:31.470 --> 00:24:32.538 align:middle line:84%
And if you have --
if you do this

00:24:32.538 --> 00:24:33.606 align:middle line:90%
for your own aggrandizement.

00:24:33.606 --> 00:24:35.241 align:middle line:90%
So if the ego comes in.

00:24:35.241 --> 00:24:39.445 align:middle line:84%
And if you use magic for
your own personal gain,

00:24:39.445 --> 00:24:41.247 align:middle line:84%
then it has a tendency
of bouncing back at you.

00:24:41.247 --> 00:24:42.181 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:24:42.181 --> 00:24:43.449 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: If you
know what I mean.

00:24:43.449 --> 00:24:45.351 align:middle line:84%
So my aim is that -- to
allow magic back in the world

00:24:45.351 --> 00:24:49.021 align:middle line:84%
in a very safe way, if
you know what I mean.

00:24:49.021 --> 00:24:51.290 align:middle line:84%
And whatever magic you
bring into the world --

00:24:51.290 --> 00:24:53.960 align:middle line:84%
if there's any black magic --
white magic is so much stronger.

00:24:53.960 --> 00:24:56.262 align:middle line:84%
So it's kind of intrinsically
safe.

00:24:56.262 --> 00:24:57.463 align:middle line:90%
If you know what I mean.

00:24:57.463 --> 00:24:59.065 align:middle line:84%
But your -- if you're
harboring a fear, it's --

00:24:59.065 --> 00:25:02.368 align:middle line:84%
it can be a little bit dangerous
to go down that kind of road.

00:25:02.368 --> 00:25:05.905 align:middle line:84%
But if you're harboring ego,
and if you want to use magic

00:25:05.905 --> 00:25:09.875 align:middle line:84%
to better your own position,
then it has a tendency

00:25:09.875 --> 00:25:11.744 align:middle line:90%
of just bouncing back at you.

00:25:11.744 --> 00:25:12.578 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Hmm.

00:25:12.578 --> 00:25:13.679 align:middle line:90%
>> Evans: And I love that phrase

00:25:13.679 --> 00:25:18.217 align:middle line:84%
that magic is not --
it's entrusted to us.

00:25:18.217 --> 00:25:19.552 align:middle line:90%
And it comes through us.

00:25:19.552 --> 00:25:21.354 align:middle line:90%
We don't own it.

00:25:21.354 --> 00:25:23.823 align:middle line:84%
And I've got this
sneaking suspicion

00:25:23.823 --> 00:25:25.558 align:middle line:84%
that you're only
given enough magic

00:25:25.558 --> 00:25:26.792 align:middle line:90%
that you can be trusted with.

00:25:26.792 --> 00:25:28.027 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Mm-hmm.

00:25:28.027 --> 00:25:29.128 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: And if someone
does give you a bit of magic

00:25:29.128 --> 00:25:30.229 align:middle line:90%
that you're not ready for yet,

00:25:30.229 --> 00:25:31.764 align:middle line:84%
then it just bounces
back a little bit just

00:25:31.764 --> 00:25:32.932 align:middle line:90%
to tell you, just not yet.

00:25:32.932 --> 00:25:33.566 align:middle line:90%
If you know what I mean.

00:25:33.566 --> 00:25:34.333 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:25:34.333 --> 00:25:35.534 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Life is perfect.

00:25:35.534 --> 00:25:37.169 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Life is
intrinsically safe and perfect.

00:25:37.169 --> 00:25:38.304 align:middle line:90%
Yeah [chuckles].

00:25:38.304 --> 00:25:39.772 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: [Chuckles] you
look like a little bit

00:25:39.772 --> 00:25:41.307 align:middle line:90%
like a wizard don't you?

00:25:41.307 --> 00:25:42.508 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Well people
call me that.

00:25:42.508 --> 00:25:44.276 align:middle line:84%
I've got one client that
calls me Dumbledore,

00:25:44.276 --> 00:25:45.511 align:middle line:90%
which is [chuckles] funny.

00:25:45.511 --> 00:25:47.079 align:middle line:84%
But just for my sense
of balance,

00:25:47.079 --> 00:25:49.148 align:middle line:84%
my partner calls me
Dobby the House Elf,

00:25:49.148 --> 00:25:50.416 align:middle line:84%
just to ground me
at the weekend.

00:25:50.416 --> 00:25:51.484 align:middle line:90%
So yeah.

00:25:51.484 --> 00:25:52.785 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: That's wonderful.

00:25:52.785 --> 00:25:56.889 align:middle line:84%
What are some other concepts
that you go into or things

00:25:56.889 --> 00:25:58.591 align:middle line:84%
that we should know,
for example,

00:25:58.591 --> 00:26:00.960 align:middle line:84%
that we don't really
know in our society.

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:03.562 align:middle line:90%
In our humanness?

00:26:03.562 --> 00:26:05.164 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Well I think
there's a big concept

00:26:05.164 --> 00:26:07.466 align:middle line:90%
which is kind of interesting.

00:26:07.466 --> 00:26:09.735 align:middle line:90%
It's that we have an illusion

00:26:09.735 --> 00:26:13.606 align:middle line:84%
that Tom is Tom and
Lilou is Lilou.

00:26:13.606 --> 00:26:15.374 align:middle line:84%
And what happens
when we incarnate --

00:26:15.374 --> 00:26:19.412 align:middle line:84%
and I found this out by when
I started looking in the --

00:26:19.412 --> 00:26:21.347 align:middle line:90%
more working with the aura.

00:26:21.347 --> 00:26:25.885 align:middle line:84%
Is that we're an assemblage of
entities -- of spirit entities.

00:26:25.885 --> 00:26:27.687 align:middle line:84%
So one goes to the
head and says, I'll --

00:26:27.687 --> 00:26:30.256 align:middle line:84%
for this incarnation
I'll do the head stuff.

00:26:30.256 --> 00:26:32.525 align:middle line:84%
Another one goes to the heart
and works in the heart center.

00:26:32.525 --> 00:26:34.160 align:middle line:84%
Another goes down
to the gut center.

00:26:34.160 --> 00:26:37.396 align:middle line:84%
They sit around our main chakra
points if you know what I mean.

00:26:37.396 --> 00:26:41.300 align:middle line:84%
And then we have our guidance
that maybe is not incarnate

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:45.671 align:middle line:84%
that sits either our cerebellum
or just above our head here.

00:26:45.671 --> 00:26:50.509 align:middle line:84%
So we're an assemblage of spirit
entities all experiencing the

00:26:50.509 --> 00:26:51.644 align:middle line:90%
human condition together.

00:26:51.644 --> 00:26:53.245 align:middle line:90%
And one of them might be --

00:26:53.245 --> 00:26:56.782 align:middle line:84%
in our gut guiding us, the other
might be in our heart, loving.

00:26:56.782 --> 00:26:57.717 align:middle line:90%
And this sort of stuff.

00:26:57.717 --> 00:26:59.618 align:middle line:84%
And when we're not
feeling great,

00:26:59.618 --> 00:27:02.855 align:middle line:84%
what you can do is do what I
call a soul part integration.

00:27:02.855 --> 00:27:05.691 align:middle line:84%
And we can take a part
that is not functioning.

00:27:05.691 --> 00:27:07.793 align:middle line:84%
And we can change --
either change it's function;

00:27:07.793 --> 00:27:09.228 align:middle line:90%
give it a new job to do.

00:27:09.228 --> 00:27:10.963 align:middle line:90%
Or we can move its position

00:27:10.963 --> 00:27:14.667 align:middle line:84%
and we can install other
soul parts as well.

00:27:14.667 --> 00:27:15.868 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Hmm.

00:27:15.868 --> 00:27:17.069 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: So let's say
you want to write a book.

00:27:17.069 --> 00:27:20.039 align:middle line:84%
And you didn't feel that
you could write the book.

00:27:20.039 --> 00:27:21.907 align:middle line:84%
We could actually say, well
let's bring an intelligence

00:27:21.907 --> 00:27:25.678 align:middle line:84%
in that knows how to write a
book and we can install it.

00:27:25.678 --> 00:27:26.712 align:middle line:90%
And this is great work.

00:27:26.712 --> 00:27:27.847 align:middle line:90%
It's great fun.

00:27:27.847 --> 00:27:28.647 align:middle line:84%
It's like Lego bricks
for the soul [chuckles]

00:27:28.647 --> 00:27:30.549 align:middle line:90%
if you know what I mean?

00:27:30.549 --> 00:27:31.751 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:27:31.751 --> 00:27:34.353 align:middle line:84%
So why -- how about if you
don't know who to call?

00:27:34.353 --> 00:27:37.289 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Well I do this work
and some of the people I work

00:27:37.289 --> 00:27:39.658 align:middle line:84%
with are practitioners
of it as well.

00:27:39.658 --> 00:27:41.026 align:middle line:90%
And we all work over Skype,

00:27:41.026 --> 00:27:42.194 align:middle line:84%
so we can do it anywhere
in the world --

00:27:42.194 --> 00:27:43.129 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah?

00:27:43.129 --> 00:27:43.562 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: -- which
is kind of good.

00:27:43.562 --> 00:27:44.930 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:27:44.930 --> 00:27:47.433 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Can you just call
good light beings, wonderful,

00:27:47.433 --> 00:27:49.835 align:middle line:84%
beautiful, loving
entities to help?

00:27:49.835 --> 00:27:52.138 align:middle line:84%
And kind of they
figure out who's who.

00:27:52.138 --> 00:27:53.139 align:middle line:90%
And what's for what?

00:27:53.139 --> 00:27:54.507 align:middle line:90%
>> Evans: You can, yes.

00:27:54.507 --> 00:27:55.641 align:middle line:84%
So just decide what you want
to do and what you want to be.

00:27:55.641 --> 00:27:56.475 align:middle line:90%
So --

00:27:56.475 --> 00:27:57.243 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: You have to be clear?

00:27:57.243 --> 00:27:57.777 align:middle line:90%
>> Evans: Yeah.

00:27:57.777 --> 00:27:58.844 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:27:58.844 --> 00:28:00.846 align:middle line:84%
Or you might say, I
just want guidance.

00:28:00.846 --> 00:28:02.047 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Yeah.

00:28:02.047 --> 00:28:03.349 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: And bring it
in so it's not specific.

00:28:03.349 --> 00:28:05.384 align:middle line:84%
And then that guidance
will just pop straight in.

00:28:05.384 --> 00:28:06.752 align:middle line:90%
So whatever you need to do.

00:28:06.752 --> 00:28:09.255 align:middle line:90%
Or you might see external signs.

00:28:09.255 --> 00:28:11.824 align:middle line:84%
So you might say, look
I need some information

00:28:11.824 --> 00:28:12.825 align:middle line:90%
of the direction to go in.

00:28:12.825 --> 00:28:13.893 align:middle line:90%
And then you might see a sign.

00:28:13.893 --> 00:28:15.294 align:middle line:84%
You might see a number
on a number plate.

00:28:15.294 --> 00:28:17.530 align:middle line:84%
You might see something in a
newspaper and that sort of --

00:28:17.530 --> 00:28:19.899 align:middle line:84%
so for instance, I wanted one
of my books to be published.

00:28:19.899 --> 00:28:24.203 align:middle line:84%
And I had my -- I put my
submission into two publishers

00:28:24.203 --> 00:28:26.539 align:middle line:84%
and they both sat
on it for 3 months.

00:28:26.539 --> 00:28:28.274 align:middle line:90%
And I said, let's just see.

00:28:28.274 --> 00:28:30.643 align:middle line:84%
I need a response on this and I
want to get this book out there.

00:28:30.643 --> 00:28:34.180 align:middle line:84%
Asked for a sign, and within
one week I met 3 authors

00:28:34.180 --> 00:28:37.082 align:middle line:84%
that had all published
with this other publisher.

00:28:37.082 --> 00:28:38.284 align:middle line:90%
And so I submitted the book.

00:28:38.284 --> 00:28:40.452 align:middle line:84%
Within 48 hours I had
a publishing contract.

00:28:40.452 --> 00:28:44.123 align:middle line:84%
And without going back to the
original two publishers, some --

00:28:44.123 --> 00:28:45.958 align:middle line:84%
they picked something up and
they both wrote to me saying

00:28:45.958 --> 00:28:47.693 align:middle line:90%
that we're not interested now.

00:28:47.693 --> 00:28:50.529 align:middle line:84%
So just ask for guidance
and it will be given.

00:28:50.529 --> 00:28:51.530 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: Hmm.

00:28:51.530 --> 00:28:54.500 align:middle line:84%
I heard you say super
consciousness.

00:28:54.500 --> 00:28:56.168 align:middle line:90%
What do you mean by that?

00:28:56.168 --> 00:28:57.369 align:middle line:84%
>> Evans: Well you
know we've got the idea

00:28:57.369 --> 00:28:58.671 align:middle line:90%
about consciousness.

00:28:58.671 --> 00:28:59.705 align:middle line:90%
This self awareness.

00:28:59.705 --> 00:29:02.808 align:middle line:84%
We've got the idea
of unconsciousness.

00:29:02.808 --> 00:29:03.943 align:middle line:84%
Which is all the
things we don't know.

00:29:03.943 --> 00:29:05.711 align:middle line:84%
So you're not aware of
your big toe right now,

00:29:05.711 --> 00:29:06.712 align:middle line:90%
until I mention it.

00:29:06.712 --> 00:29:07.613 align:middle line:84%
And then you're aware
of your big toe

00:29:07.613 --> 00:29:08.981 align:middle line:90%
and all that kind of stuff.

00:29:08.981 --> 00:29:12.117 align:middle line:84%
You know. You're at a party and
then someone says your name,

00:29:12.117 --> 00:29:13.485 align:middle line:90%
Tom or Lilou, then all

00:29:13.485 --> 00:29:16.755 align:middle line:84%
of a sudden your unconscious
mind tells your conscious mind

00:29:16.755 --> 00:29:19.391 align:middle line:84%
to direct itself
in that direction.

00:29:19.391 --> 00:29:22.995 align:middle line:84%
The super-consciousness
is kind of a big concept.

00:29:22.995 --> 00:29:24.964 align:middle line:84%
Lots of people have
popularized it.

00:29:24.964 --> 00:29:28.334 align:middle line:84%
The mystics and sages of the
ages might call it Brahman

00:29:28.334 --> 00:29:29.735 align:middle line:90%
or something like that.

00:29:29.735 --> 00:29:32.705 align:middle line:84%
And Carl Young called it I think
the "Collective Unconscious".

00:29:32.705 --> 00:29:34.440 align:middle line:84%
I call it the
super-consciousness

00:29:34.440 --> 00:29:36.942 align:middle line:84%
because I think it's
a higher state, again.

00:29:36.942 --> 00:29:42.581 align:middle line:84%
And it's all of our thoughts and
memories from the past, present,

00:29:42.581 --> 00:29:44.116 align:middle line:90%
and future all collected there.

00:29:44.116 --> 00:29:46.318 align:middle line:84%
So other people call it the
neurosphere

00:29:46.318 --> 00:29:50.389 align:middle line:84%
that there's a theory that the
planet Earth is like a framework

00:29:50.389 --> 00:29:52.458 align:middle line:90%
which stores all this energy.

00:29:52.458 --> 00:29:54.827 align:middle line:84%
Other people call
it the I-field --

00:29:54.827 --> 00:29:56.562 align:middle line:84%
Irving Laslow calls it the
I-field --

00:29:56.562 --> 00:29:57.930 align:middle line:90%
the information field.

00:29:57.930 --> 00:30:00.232 align:middle line:84%
Some people refer it to
the Zero Point Field.

00:30:00.232 --> 00:30:03.202 align:middle line:84%
So what I like at the moment
is like the quantum physicists

